title: Piano Magic - Dark Horses EP (2008) (320 Kbps)
description:
Piano Magic release a new 4-track EP on October 27th 2008. &#039;Dark Horses&#039; was recorded, mixed and mastered at Sound Solution in Hackney, London. It will be released on the Make Mine Music label and be strictly limited to 1000 copies.

The tracklisting is :

1) Dark Horses
2) Stations
3) Vacancies
4) A Book I Should Not Read

Personnel for the tracks were Franck Alba, Angele David-Guillou, Glen Johnson, Cedric Pin, Alasdair Steer and Jerome Tcherneyan.
